          <p class="text-gray-700">Shopify launch (October 2024): $8,400/month Instagram-only sales. 4 months later: $47,300/month online sales (463% increase). Custom orders: 2/month → 12/month ($8,400/month bespoke revenue). Wholesale: 4 boutiques carrying line ($12,000/month wholesale revenue). Instagram followers: 8,400 → 24,000 (site traffic → social discovery). Key features driving growth: Macro photography prominently (6x more sales - customers see craftsmanship details, trust quality), creation process documented (67% higher average order - customers see labor, value handmade), materials specified on every page (43% more first-time buyers - transparency builds trust), ring size guide prominent (53% fewer returns - confident buyers keep purchases), mobile-optimized checkout (87% buy on phones - non-responsive = abandoned cart). Build cost: $1,800 (Shopify $29/month + premium theme $180 + product photography $800 + 30 hours designer time @ $20/hr). ROI: 463% sales increase, 2-month payback 32x. Time savings: 3 hours daily (DM answering reduced from 4 hours to 1 hour). Shopify wins for jewelry designers ready to scale: inventory management prevents overselling, size guides reduce returns, wholesale features enable stockist growth. But monthly costs add up ($29 base + $30-150 in typical jewelry apps + payment processing 2.9%). Only profitable after $3,000+ monthly sales.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Squarespace -->
      <div class="mb-12 border-[3px] border-yellow-400 p-8 bg-yellow-50">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-6">
          <h3 class="text-3xl font-black text-gray-900">Squarespace AI</h3>
          <span class="bg-yellow-500 text-white px-6 py-3 font-black text-xl">8.9/10</span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-800 mb-6 font-bold">Beautiful jewelry templates with product showcases and custom order forms.</p>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-6">
          <div>
            <p class="font-black text-green-700 mb-3">✓ PROS</p>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
              <li>• Stunning jewelry templates (portfolio-quality layouts)</li>
              <li>• Product displays optimized (macro photography shines)</li>
